      <summary>What is box build?<span class="sc-faq-mk">+</span></summary>
      <div class="sc-faq-a">Assembling the complete product beyond the circuit board — fitting the PCBA into its enclosure, adding cables/harnesses and mechanical parts, sealing it, and producing a finished, tested unit.</div>
